sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User Browser
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend Django Auth
    participant A42 as API 42

    U->>FE: Open login page
    FE->>BE: GET /api/auth/42/login/
    BE-->>U: Redirect to API 42 authorize URL with state

    U->>A42: Authenticate and grant consent
    A42-->>BE: Callback with code and state
    BE->>BE: Validate state
    BE->>A42: Exchange code for access token
    A42-->>BE: Return access token
    BE->>A42: Request user profile
    A42-->>BE: Return user profile payload

    BE->>BE: Upsert local user and campus user
    BE-->>U: Set access and refresh cookies, redirect to app

    U->>FE: Load authenticated app
    FE->>BE: GET /api/auth/profile/
    BE-->>FE: 200 profile

    Note over FE,BE: Access token eventually expires
    FE->>BE: Call protected endpoint
    BE-->>FE: 401 unauthorized
    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/token/refresh/

    alt Refresh token is valid
        BE-->>FE: 200 and new access cookie
        FE->>BE: Retry protected request
        BE-->>FE: 200 success
    else Refresh token is invalid
        BE-->>FE: 401 and clear auth cookies
        FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/logout/
        BE-->>FE: 200 logged out
    end